item.title: Global fossil fuel policy tracker application
item.description: Project Details The objective of the Fossil Fuel Non-Proliferation Tracker is to identify, gather, filter, categorise and visualise supply-side policies on a global scale, while also providing granular insight within each country on the actors involved in furthering supply-side policies.
